---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../index.css';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions - CozyPixels" description="Terms and conditions for using CozyPixels wallpapers and software.">
  <main style="padding: 120px 24px 80px; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
    <div style="max-width: 720px; width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 1.7;">
      <h1 class="font-display" style="font-size: 3.5rem; color: #1e2444; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 850; letter-spacing: -0.04em;">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #7a84a0; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; font-family: var(--font-label); letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;">Last updated: May 31, 2026</p>
      
      <p style="color: #52607a; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">By accessing and using CozyPixels (the Website, Desktop App, and Chrome Extension), you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; font-weight: 700;">1. Use of Wallpapers</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">All wallpapers hosted on CozyPixels are provided for <strong style="color: #1e2444;">personal, non-commercial use only</strong>. While CozyPixels curates these images and provides software to manage them, the copyright of the original artworks remains with their respective artists and creators. You may not sell, redistribute, or use these wallpapers for commercial purposes without explicit permission from the original artists.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; font-weight: 700;">2. Software Usage</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">The CozyPixels Desktop Application and Chrome Extension are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We are not liable for any damages or data loss that may occur while using our software.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; font-weight: 700;">3. Open Source</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Portions of CozyPixels are open-source. Please refer to our GitHub repository for specific licenses regarding our source code.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; font-weight: 700;">4. Contact</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">If you have any questions regarding these terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@cozypixels.app" style="color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">legal@cozypixels.app</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
